<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Covert1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Covert,</orth> subst., thicket: <cit><quote>you must retire yourself into some c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.664" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 664</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>in this c. will we make our stand,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 1, 3</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>stole into the c. of the wood,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 1.1.132" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 1, 132</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>